item.description: Hello there! My name is Phan Vũ-Tinh, can call me Aaron. I’m a Vietnamese mobile engineer, working mostly on iOS app native development. Besides, I’m also a runner, a travel enthusiast, a bookworm, a pluviophile, and … a superhero movie die-hard fan :) I’m passionate about learning new things, deciphering challenging problems, breaking impasses, and creating delightful experiences. This blog was made to learn and to share.
